M|Key |**Vi|**
M|Key |tx|```
M|Key |tx|K = Invitations × Conversion Rate
M|Key |tx|K > 1 = Viral growth (each us brings more than 1 new us)
M|Key |tx|K < 1 = Amplified growth (referrals supplement other acquisition)
M|Key |tx|```
M|Key |**Ex|**
